@import ./_tui.convo

> user
Implement diff rendering for `ConvoTuiCtrl`.

Goals:
- Stop writing the entire screen on every render when only a subset of characters changed.
- Compare the back buffer to the front buffer and only write changed runs to stdout.
- Preserve the current behavior of full redraw on first render and after buffer resize.
- Keep ANSI style changes correct for foreground/background colors.
- Keep the implementation simple and readable.
- Avoid changing public APIs unless needed.

Acceptance criteria:
- `render()` still clears and draws into the back buffer.
- Changed characters are emitted using cursor positioning escape sequences.
- Unchanged characters are not emitted.
- The front buffer is updated after rendering.
- Resize still forces a full redraw.
- Dispose/cleanup behavior is unchanged.

Update notes at the end of your response
